snippet.title: BEST FAILS! Epic Fails | You'll LAUGH all day long! | MAY 2018 Edition
snippet.description:
The BEST FAILS brings you the NEW FUNNIEST FAILS COMPILATION of 2018!  Enjoy this candid funny montage of the best slips, falls, crashes, impacts, hits, punches, fights, fails and bails!
The Best Fails brings you the best funny vines compilations, try not to laugh challenges, fails, wins, and hilarious viral videos.  We find the best new dank memes, bloopers, funny clips, and you laugh you lose challenges in order to create an army of fails, life awesome moments, and epic wins.  New Videos Weekly and Monthly!
